title: Spittin' Chiclets Episode 3: Habs, McDavid, Rolling Stones and more
description:
Episode 3 features Rear Admiral & Ryan Whitney talking about the Habs hot start, Connor McDavid, Patrick Laine, and Rear Admiral tells a Rolling Stones stalking story.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/schiclets
